{"tid":1088543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港銀行體系結餘　一月三次　清倉　危險","createTime":"2019-04-02T06:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T04:10:27.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b5fde2c38baf86f7ed9844a308a8ade0dded2a","tid":1088543,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156623718069934&amp;set=a.10156336969309934&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156623718069934%26set%3Da.10156336969309934%26type%3D3&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m67QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=62e2bb22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156623718069934&amp;set=a.10156336969309934&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n我諗好多人都冇留意呢啲消息，其實銀行體系結餘由去年$1800億，不斷俾人「洗劫」，這幾個星期速度超級加快，而且好狠好兇！剛才又冇咗50億，現在剩返540億！（早兩日仲有680億）<br />\n<br />\n「颱風」將至，大家請提醒身邊朋友做好「防風措施」，各安天命，好自為之。<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tfb/1/16/1f64f_1f3fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftfb%2F1%2F16%2F1f64f_1f3fb.png&h=1e4801cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tfb/1/16/1f64f_1f3fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftfb%2F1%2F16%2F1f64f_1f3fb.png&h=1e4801cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ruxz7S2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fruxz7S2.jpg&h=c1b74128&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69da778723fd7b2280f76cdef8285fff45c4a5da","tid":1088543,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"香港於2019年2月底的外匯儲備資產為4,273億美元<br />\n<br />\n仲有排頂"},{"pid":"807e3c46db9cf50e5f6269ee2808b62fafc02d87","tid":1088543,"uid":42340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-